descriptionHtml:
---Description---

These mods will give you a head start in the game to say. For the people that think it\'s odd that you start off weak barely knowing any skills. I mean like in your 30\'s-40\'s when you start the game right? Anyways use these simple archetypes to craft a well skilled starter character right from the get go.

Will add more later. If people are interested in the idea of using these.

---Archetypes---

Warrior:
This will level you up to 10 and level up your One-Handed, Block, Archery, and Light armor. 

Also it will give you the perks within each skill that you are able to get with your level; without using the perk points that you obtain leveling up to 10.
This mean you will have about 9 perks to distribute to other skills right from the start.

---How to use---

Simply put the text file in your Skyrim folder( The same folder that the data folder is located). 
Make a new character and once you get your hands are unbound type bat \"File name\" in the console. (Example: \"bat Warrior\") This will level you up to 10 and give you basic warrior skills and perks.
